  "prompt": "How many people have a net worth of 20 million dollars?",
  "response": "As of the latest estimates, the number of individuals with a net worth of $20 million or more varies by source and can change frequently due to fluctuations in asset values. According to reports from wealth research firms like Wealth-X or Spectrem Group, there were approximately several hundred thousand ultra-high-net-worth individuals (UHNWIs) globally, defined as those with a net worth of at least $30 million. Those with a net worth of $20 million would be a subset of this group.\n\nFor the most accurate and current figures, consulting the latest reports from these wealth measurement organizations or financial services firms would be beneficial, as they typically publish annual reports on global wealth distribution.",
